{"tid":1592552,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"習慣番工既時候 係咪代表人生已完","createTime":"2019-09-24T16:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T16:09:53.000Z","uid":93540,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"71af29570168a65cf2d70de35b78d6c2da36b1a5","tid":1592552,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:09:42.000Z","msg":"今年21歲 出左黎做野一年幾<br />\n每日都好攰好唔想番 但同時又慣左番工既生活<br />\n幾攰都係咁起身番工 <br />\n好想打機但諗到聽日要番工都係乖乖地去訓教<br />\n放假有時間都只係想訓耐啲 hea全日<br />\n好想落街打波但真係有心無力<br />\n讀書既日子真係人生最開心既時間<br />\n想做咩就做 隨時都可以去玩去拍拖<br />\n真係好想以後都可以咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8903e8d1af0a91b2700b3db124b053f2b003d3","tid":1592552,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:09:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"}]}